# Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [Date]

## Introduction

Welcome to Chirpers ("we," "our," or "us"). At Chirper, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled responsibly. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and disclose your personal information when you use our messaging application.

Please take a moment to review this Privacy Policy to understand our practices regarding your personal data. By using our application, you agree to the terms and practices described in this Privacy Policy.

## Information We Collect

### Registration Information

When you create an account with [Your Messaging App Name], we may collect the following information:

- Your name
- Email address
- Username
- Messages


### Messages and Content

When you use our messaging services, we collect and store the messages, photos, videos, and other content that you send and receive.

### Usage Information

We may collect information about how you use our app, including:

- Log data (e.g., app crashes, usage statistics)


### Contacts

With your permission, we may access your device's contact list to help you find and connect with your contacts on our platform.

## How We Use Your Information

We use your personal information for the following purposes:

- To provide, maintain, and improve our messaging services.
- To personalize your experience and enhance our app's features.
- To communicate with you, including responding to your inquiries and providing customer support.
- To send you important notifications and updates related to our services.
- To analyze and improve our app's performance and user experience.
- To ensure the security and integrity of our messaging platform.

## Data Security

We take data security seriously and implement appropriate measures to protect your personal information. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure. While we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

## Sharing Your Information

We do not share your personal information with third parties unless required for legal reasons or to provide our services. We may share your information with:

- Service providers and partners who help us deliver our services.
- Law enforcement agencies or legal authorities when required by law.
- Other users in the context of your messaging interactions.

## Your Choices

- You can update or delete your account information at any time through the app's settings.
- You may have the option to opt-out of certain data collection and marketing communications.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or data practices, please contact us at shajeelyahya@gmail.com.

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Please review it periodically to stay informed about our data practices and any changes.

Thank you for using Chirper!
